{"tid":1423382,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友為左個女仔朋友講分手","createTime":"2019-08-06T13:45:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T04:52:50.000Z","uid":217730,"like":191,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a0f11a3bdb2907f2734b2a764874cafcbc598af1","tid":1423382,"uid":217730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:45:11.000Z","msg":"早排同男朋友出街<br />\n見到佢有個女仔朋友whatsapp佢問佢一啲學校嘅嘢<br />\n咁我就叫佢禁入去睇下啦<br />\n一開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左岩岩問嘢個句之外係冇哂之前啲record<br />\n然後我問佢點解冇哂record<br />\n佢話whatsapp壞左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我再叫佢開下其他人d record睇下係咪真係壞左<br />\n明明其他人d record仲係哂度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淨係同女仔d whatsapp record冇哂<br />\n咁我問我男朋友佢地傾左啲咩啦<br />\n佢叫佢個女仔朋友cap record<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：我唔知佢地之前傾過啲咩<br />\n個女仔一嚟就覆：唔好痴線啦你地 我地絕左交架喇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我嬲到爆炸叫我男朋友block左個女仔<br />\n佢block完之後個女仔踢左佢出佢地個common whatsapp group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我男朋友就嬲左我<br />\n話我搞到佢冇哂啲朋友<br />\n話一定會add翻個女仔同佢解釋清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後男朋友打比個女仔同佢傾<br />\n個女仔原諒左佢<br />\n仲add翻佢private ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底係我諗多左定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正皮：條女小學雞 佢兩個一定有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n負皮：普通朋友啫 正常社交喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3f63beff17f2fe67e3b064760f904b88addfe8","tid":1423382,"uid":217730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0f11a3bdb2907f2734b2a764874cafcbc598af1","tid":1423382,"uid":217730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:45:11.000Z","msg":"早排同男朋友出街<br />\n見到佢有個女仔朋友whatsapp佢問佢一啲學校嘅嘢<br />\n咁我就叫佢禁入去睇下啦<br />\n一開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左岩岩問嘢個句之外係冇哂之前啲record<br />\n然後我問佢點解冇哂record<br />\n佢話whatsapp壞左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我再叫佢開下其他人d record睇下係咪真係壞左<br />\n明明其他人d record仲係哂度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淨係同女仔d whatsapp record冇哂<br />\n咁我問我男朋友佢地傾左啲咩啦<br />\n佢叫佢個女仔朋友cap record<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：我唔知佢地之前傾過啲咩<br />\n個女仔一嚟就覆：唔好痴線啦你地 我地絕左交架喇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" clas